<dd>&nbsp;&nbsp; Фото (<a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/deed.en">Creative Commons license</a>): <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/wagner-machado-carlos-lemes/2034990391/">Wagner Machado Carlos Lemes</a> 
